{"tid":377973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地男女打風行山遇險求助　葛珮帆批累己累人、無知自私","createTime":"2017-08-28T06:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T10:27:18.000Z","uid":51904,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd55ec1761208b582f8d40072c4e770ebe4c384b","tid":377973,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"強烈熱帶風暴「帕卡」襲港期間，一對內地男女採「非正常路徑」上飛鵝山行山被困，致電求助，逾百名消防及救護人員花25小時，終將兩人救出送院，惟其中一名消防隊目受傷。事件引起關注，民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆今早在facebook分享相關報道，批評「盲摸摸去行山會累己累人」，又認為打風時「追風」、「看浪」、「行山」，都「好無知又自私」。<br />\n<br />\n其黨友蔣麗芸昨亦在facebook慨嘆，「打風行山，又辛苦了消防英雄！」"},{"pid":"7f7bfd05071791f4cb7020545ae981fbc0dd8a01","tid":377973,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"建制派平時好幫大陸人架,狗咬狗?"},{"pid":"25667b5f75b27abce70c6128f6ac48168bca075f","tid":377973,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T07:16:58.000Z","msg":"傷害十三億人的感情！"},{"pid":"cd2b5db999b25847c6a4ebbfea78e5b8e6bd20ee","tid":377973,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026d4538d8a74ef122c17b204d42f673e29dffbb","tid":377973,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T07:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f8/Digimonq.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/190?cb=20100712092436\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff8%2FDigimonq.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F190%3Fcb%3D20100712092436&h=9e7b0531&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"940d2ed24d4e9c17957c64936f34c0020e17c8b0","tid":377973,"uid":111909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T0